      "ingredients": "<ul>\n<li>\n<span>Acids:</span> fruit AHA, salicylic BHA </li>\n<li><span>Aloe Vera</span></li>\n<li><span>Water</span></li>\n<li><span>Oils:</span> jojoba, borago (all skin-friendly oils)</li>\n<li><span>Essential oils:</span> neroli, litsea, palmarosa</li>\n<li><span>Preservatives:</span> sorbic acid (natural preservative), benzoic acid (natural preservative), dehydracetic acid (natural preservative), benzyl alcohol (natural preservative), CO2 rosemary extract (antioxidant)</li>\n<li><span>Emulsifiers:</span> sodium stearoyl lactylate, xanthan copper, stearic acid (natural emulsifiers that mix oils and aloe)</li>\n</ul>",
      "shortDescription": "Your skin needs enhanced regeneration and craves active and effective ingredients, that’s why we have added EXFOLIATE MY SKIN to your treatment, enriched with AHA and BHA natural acids.\n<aside>What do you need AHA (glycolic, lactic, malic, citric) acids for? They will exfoliate your skin, help retain moisture, stimulate the production of ceramides and collagen, and help get rid of pigmentation.\n<br/>BHA acids (for example, salicylic) unlike AHAs, are fat-soluble and, therefore, can penetrate into the deeper layers of your skin. It has excellent antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties, reduces the production of sebum, renews your skin, relieves any inflammation and promotes healing of acne scars as well. Do you know what's even better? It also smoothes out fine wrinkles and evens out the relief of your skin. Isn't it amazing?!</aside>"
