      "shortDescription": "We've figured out that the lipid layer of your skin is slightly off. Therefore, we added a complex of non-pore-blocking light oils NOURISH MY SKIN to your treatment. \nHow's it going to help you? Well, it contains vitamin E, nutritious oils of grape seed, evening primrose, hazelnut, macadamia, jojoba, hemp, pomegranate, borago, argan, rice - these guys are so rich with antioxidants, they will nourish your skin and help with sebum regulation. <aside>As a result, your skin will stop producing any excess fat and you will get rid of that oily shine. \nEssential oils of mandarin, sweet orange and lemon will even out the skin tone, reduce rosacea, will accelerate the recovery of your skin as well as help other components do they job better.</aside>",
