    "description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Taping is a fast and effective method of rejuvenation without injections or surgery. And it works at different deep levels - at the level of lymph, muscles, fat packs and skin. During this course you will learn how to work at all these levels.\n<br/>The magic of the taping technique is that it works even when you sleep.😊</p>\n<div class=\"contentBox\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<h2>The course will help to</h2>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>define the face shape</li>\n<li>relax muscles</li>\n<li>reduce crow's feet and nasolabial folds</li>\n<li>enhance the effect of massage</li>\n<li>remove swelling</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
    "feedbacks": "[\n    \"Hello, Alena!\nThis January my cosmetologist told me that only an injection would save my eyebrow. But I was not ready to do it at all. That's why I was waiting for your course on tapes. Yesterday I finally received it and I immediately watched the video, placed the tapes on my brow and forehead areas for the whole night. It's amazing! No wrinkles in the morning! Thank you for helping to maintain youth without additional intervention 🌼🌼🌼 \",\n    \"I also wanted to write about tapes. I'm shocked. Really shocked!! I did it at night and when I took them off in the morning I just didn't believe it. I woke my husband up and started poking my forehead saying \\\"They are invisible now!\\\" They disappeared. My deep wrinkles are gone❤️❤️❤️ I spent the whole day under the impression. I will definitely take a photo before and after😊\nThe wrinkles on my forehead are my pain. I frown and the creases are so deep. And now they disappeared. My poor friends, I've been sending them photos all day long.\nHow beautiful I am without these wrinkles 😀 \",\n    \"Today I did an eyes lifting and the swelling disappeared as it never was there. I was trying to achieve this effect for a long time and finally succeeded!\nI'm just so delighted)). Now I have my own magic remedy for edema😊 \",\n    \"Alena, I wanted to tell you that the video course is a bomb! Awesome. I am so happy!! 😊 I learned a lot of new and useful things)) I didn’t regret that I bought it even for a second😊\"\n]",
    "shortDescription": "<p>Taping is a fast and effective method of rejuvenation without injections and surgical intervention. And it works at different deep levels - at the level of lymph, muscles, fat packs and the skin. And on the course you will learn to work at all these levels 😊</p>\n<p>Course author $t(products:video.authorChichuk)</p>\n<h2>WHERE TO BUY TAPES?</h2>\n<p>In the EU, they can be ordered from Amazon: <a target=\"_ blank\" href=\"https://www.amazon.de/dp/B06XKCRNVV/ref=as_sl_pc_qf_sp_asin_til?tag=creamly-21&linkCode=w00&linkId=652988736d2\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">K-Active Tape Elite</a>\n</p>\n<p>Brands we recommend on the course:</p>\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\n<li><strong>K-active</strong>: cotton, width 5 cm (beige - hypoallergenic)</li>\n<li><strong>Cure tape</strong>: cotton, width 5 cm</li>\n<li><strong>BBalance</strong>: face tape, cotton, width 5 cm</li>\n<li><strong>BBtape</strong>: cotton, 5 cm wide</li>\n</ul>",
